Class FoodItem

java.lang.Object
FoodItem
public class FoodItem extends Object
The FoodItem class represents a food item object It contains information about the food item including a unique ID, a reference to the associated FoodProduct, and an expiry date. It also has the getters and setters for the different attributes, a method to generate an HTML string and a method to generate a string representation.
Version:
1.2
Author:
Chaima Jebri
